additionalProperty.value:
INGREDIENTS: White Bread, Garlic Margarine Spread (20%)

White Bread contains: Wheat Flour (Wheat Flour, Thiamin, Folic Acid), Water, Yeast, Canola Oil, Iodised Salt, Vinegar, Improver [Wheat Flour, Flour Improver (300), Amylase], Preservative (281).

Garlic and Parsley Margarine Spread Contains:  Margarine [Palm Oil**, Water, Salt, Emulsifier (471 from Palm, 472c from Palm), Natural Flavouring, Antioxidant (304), Natural Colour (160a)], Rehydrated Garlic (15%), Canola Oil, Dried Parsley, Water, Acidity Regulator (330).

description: From Coles Brand, Garlic Bread Twin Pack. It is a great addition to your meal.
name: Garlic Bread Twin Pack
